query:
SELECT t.id, t.name, COUNT(td.id) as dep_count 
FROM tasks t 
LEFT JOIN task_dependencies td ON t.id = td.taskId 
WHERE t.householdId = (SELECT id FROM households WHERE name = 'Test Invite Code')
GROUP BY t.id, t.name
HAVING dep_count > 0
LIMIT 5
